{"tid":1391540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八月五，七點半，調景嶺","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:11:17.000Z","uid":20189,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"85320ed2af569c4388a6a2ef82fbbd71dffeea15","tid":1391540,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"要人！無論地面又好，月台又好，都要大量手足！<br />\n<br />\n1. 令唔敢罷工既手足，睇到咁多人後會安心加入。再唔係用交通理由同老細講返唔到<br />\n<br />\n2. 比壓力港豬，等佢地返唔到工，公司少個人，其他有心罷工老細又唔like既就自然更安全<br />\n<br />\n3. 到時一定有班市民被迫留係站內/外，搞鏗鏘集放映會，宣揚克警英勇事蹟<br />\n<br />\n其他交通樞紐都要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f2eff44c271ec3338e6e123fe461e84d38b665","tid":1391540,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"1be59435c7de69ce04f620b189f5934fe620ba4c","tid":1391540,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【暗黑經濟學】發夢原則<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390973</a><br />\n在資源有限和時間性下，必須建築一件大夢，我們夢醒之時，敵人就再無夢可發。現在，我們要先改變造夢思維。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ce905c8d34be704d0de633fb2b6f7c8de2ad22a","tid":1391540,"uid":235515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"去下其他站得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好遠"},{"pid":"17b8c556f67737d45538a9f17072b979ff1219e2","tid":1391540,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:00:49.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"13d86f791fc56b5e9ac34f70c21892b3547d9d47","tid":1391540,"uid":243834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,